LUMEN / lumenshaders
License: MIT
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The "liquid-chrome" visual preset (shared/canvas-scene-runtime.mjs) ports the
height-field + faux normal-map anisotropic-metal technique from LUMEN's MODE0
shader. The implementation was rewritten for Sonara's WebGL 1 / GLSL ES 1.00
fullscreen u_* interface.

