Artistic references (inspiration only — no code copied)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The "fluid-volume" and "endless-shallows" presets are original
reimplementations whose look was inspired by publicly shared CodePen studies
(Sabo Sugi). No source code from those references is used or redistributed;
the shaders are written from scratch using Sonara's own shader prelude.

The cosine-palette formula used by "iridescent-bloom" follows the freely
published technique by Inigo Quilez.
